name: USA shaped stud earrings
description:
These cute USA stud earrings are the perfect gift for any lover of the US.

The details of these cutout is amazing! I chose to stain these because it really brings out the grain of the wood.

Made from Birch plywood, these bad boys measure roughly 1 inch x 0.75 inch.

Available in Dark Walnut stain or Red Mahogany.

Red Mahogany is shown in images here.

These are very lightweight and are a really cute everyday alternative to pearls or diamonds.

Comes in cotton filled jewelry box ready to gift or for safe keeping in your jewelry box.

Free shipping within the U.S.

name: Africa Stud Earrings in various colors
description:
Africa stud earrings in various colors.

Small stud earrings to match your favorite spring outfit! I made these in different bright colors to match the trend for this year.

Earrings measure 1 inch long and 1/8 of an inch.

Fastens with titanium ear posts and metal stoppers. Also available as clip ons. Just send a message stating clip ons.

These earrings ship with USPS First Class Mail.

name: Round Dorothy Dandridge Stud Earrings in various colors
description:
These resin coated glass earrings make the best stocking stuffers! featuring iconic Hollywood legend, Dorothy Dandridge in a vibrant hue, these earrings are unique and sure to be appreciated by the recipient. Perfect for the movie or history buff.

Dorothy Dandridge was an American actress and popular singer, and was the first African-American to be nominated for an Academy Award for Best Actress. She is best known for her performances in the movie Carmen Jones and the musical Porgy and Bess.

These earrings are part of InspEARation, inspiration that you wear on your ear!

*All InspEARation earrings ship in a jewelry box, I also include a card. Please note in the message to buyer if you would like it additional gift wrapping or a specific message in card.

*This item ships with USPS first class mail

*Made from 1 inch discs of glass with an image adhered with non toxic resin. all my ear posts are hypo allergenic.
